payload.text:
To upgrade the `AdCard` component with a more premium, modern design, I will:

1.  **Increase Image Size**: Make the image area taller for better visual impact.
2.  **Modernize Badges**: Move the **Price** to a bold, green badge floating on the image. Move the **Category** to a clean white badge.
3.  **Refine Typography**: Use bolder titles, clearer location indicators with icons, and relaxed line height for descriptions.
4.  **Add Hover Effects**: Implement a "lift" effect (`-translate-y-1`) and shadow expansion on hover to make the card feel interactive.

Here is the upgraded code:

# Updated files:

## components/AdCard.tsx

Completely redesigned AdCard with larger images, floating price tags, refined typography, and interactive hover animations.

```tsx
import React from 'react';
import { Ad } from '../types';

interface AdCardProps {
  ad: Ad;
  onClick: () => void;
}

export const AdCard: React.FC<AdCardProps> = ({ ad, onClick }) => {
  return (
    <div 
      onClick={onClick}
      className="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer flex flex-col h-full relative"
    >
      {/* Image Container */}
      <div className="relative h-56 w-full overflow-hidden bg-gray-100">
        {ad.images.length > 0 ? (
          <img 
            src={ad.images[0]} 
            alt={ad.title} 
            className="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500 ease-out"
          />
        ) : (
          <div className="w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-100 text-gray-400">
            <svg className="w-12 h-12 opacity-20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth={1} d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" /></svg>
          </div>
        )}

        {/* Gradient Overlay for better contrast if needed, mostly for aesthetics */}
        <div className="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/10 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300" />

        {/* Category Badge - Top Left */}
        <div className="absolute top-3 left-3">
           <span className="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-semibold bg-white/95 text-indigo-600 shadow-sm backdrop-blur-md">
             {ad.category || 'Produs'}
           </span>
        </div>

        {/* Price Tag - Bottom Right */}
        <div className="absolute bottom-3 right-3">
           <span className="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold bg-green-600 text-white shadow-lg tracking-wide">
             {ad.price.toLocaleString()} RON
           </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Content */}
      <div className="p-5 flex flex-col flex-grow">
        <div className="mb-2">
            <h3 className="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 line-clamp-1 group-hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">
                {ad.title}
            </h3>

            {/* Location Line */}
            {ad.location && (
                <div className="flex items-center text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">
                    <svg className="w-3.5 h-3.5 mr-1 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth={2} d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" /><path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth={2} d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" /></svg>
                    <span className="truncate">
                      {ad.location.city}, {ad.location.county}
                      {ad.location.village ? ` • ${ad.location.village}` : ''}
                    </span>
                </div>
            )}
        </div>

        <p className="text-sm text-gray-600 line-clamp-2 mb-4 flex-grow leading-relaxed">
            {ad.description}
        </p>

        {/* Footer */}
        <div className="pt-4 border-t border-gray-100 flex items-center justify-between mt-auto">
            <span className="text-xs text-gray-400 font-medium">
                {new Date(ad.createdAt).toLocaleDateString()}
            </span>
            <span className="inline-flex items-center text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-600 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">
                View Details 
                <svg className="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth={2} d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" /></svg>
            </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
};

To implement the "Ads along a route" feature, I will introduce a **Travel Mode** in the search filters.

Since we don't have access to a live GPS routing API (like Google Maps) in this environment, I will build a **Graph-based Routing System**. This uses a "County Adjacency Graph" to calculate the likely path between two counties.

**How it works:**
1.  **User Selects Route:** Start: `București` → End: `Prahova`.
2.  **Algorithm:** The system calculates the path using Breadth-First Search (BFS) on the county graph.
    *   *Path:* București → Ilfov → Prahova.
3.  **Result:** The user sees ads from **București**, **Ilfov**, and **Prahova** (including all villages/cities within them), effectively showing products "along the way".

### Implementation Plan:

1.  **`utils/routeGraph.ts`**: Create a new utility file containing the adjacency map of Romanian counties and the pathfinding algorithm.
2.  **`pages/Home.tsx`**:
    *   Add a Toggle Switch: "🏠 Local" vs "🚗 Travel Mode".
    *   Add "Start Point" and "End Point" dropdowns.
    *   Integrate the routing logic to filter ads based on the calculated county path.

---

# Changes

## utils/routeGraph.ts
New file. Defines the neighbors for Romanian counties and the logic to find the path between them.

```typescript
// Adjacency Graph for Romanian Counties to simulate routing
// This allows us to find "intermediate" counties between a Start and End point.

const COUNTY_ADJACENCY: { [key: string]: string[] } = {
  "Alba": ["Cluj", "Bihor", "Arad", "Hunedoara", "Sibiu", "Mureș"],
  "Arad": ["Bihor", "Alba", "Hunedoara", "Timiș"],
  "Argeș": ["Sibiu", "Vâlcea", "Olt", "Teleorman", "Dâmbovița", "Brașov"],
  "Bacău": ["Neamț", "Vaslui", "Vrancea", "Covasna", "Harghita"],
  "Bihor": ["Satu Mare", "Sălaj", "Cluj", "Alba", "Arad"],
  "Bistrița-Năsăud": ["Maramureș", "Suceava", "Mureș", "Cluj"],
  "Botoșani": ["Suceava", "Iași"],
  "Brașov": ["Mureș", "Harghita", "Covasna", "Buzău", "Prahova", "Dâmbovița", "Argeș", "Sibiu"],
  "Brăila": ["Galați", "Tulcea", "Constanța", "Ialomița", "Buzău", "Vrancea"],
  "București": ["Ilfov"],
  "Buzău": ["Vrancea", "Brăila", "Ialomița", "Prahova", "Brașov", "Covasna"],
  "Caraș-Severin": ["Timiș", "Hunedoara", "Gorj", "Mehedinți"],
  "Călărași": ["Ilfov", "Ialomița", "Constanța", "Giurgiu"],
  "Cluj": ["Sălaj", "Maramureș", "Bistrița-Năsăud", "Mureș", "Alba", "Bihor"],
  "Constanța": ["Tulcea", "Brăila", "Ialomița", "Călărași"],
  "Covasna": ["Harghita", "Bacău", "Vrancea", "Buzău", "Brașov"],
  "Dâmbovița": ["Brașov", "Prahova", "Ilfov", "Giurgiu", "Teleorman", "Argeș"],
  "Dolj": ["Mehedinți", "Gorj", "Vâlcea", "Olt"],
  "Galați": ["Vaslui", "Vrancea", "Brăila"],
  "Giurgiu": ["Teleorman", "Dâmbovița", "Ilfov", "Călărași"],
  "Gorj": ["Mehedinți", "Caraș-Severin", "Hunedoara", "Vâlcea", "Dolj"],
  "Harghita": ["Suceava", "Neamț", "Bacău", "Covasna", "Brașov", "Mureș"],
  "Hunedoara": ["Arad", "Bihor", "Alba", "Vâlcea", "Gorj", "Caraș-Severin", "Timiș"],
  "Ialomița": ["Brăila", "Constanța", "Călărași", "Ilfov", "Prahova", "Buzău"],
  "Iași": ["Botoșani", "Suceava", "Neamț", "Vaslui"],
  "Ilfov": ["Prahova", "Ialomița", "Călărași", "Giurgiu", "Dâmbovița", "București"],
  "Maramureș": ["Satu Mare", "Sălaj", "Cluj", "Bistrița-Năsăud", "Suceava"],
  "Mehedinți": ["Caraș-Severin", "Gorj", "Dolj"],
  "Mureș": ["Bistrița-Năsăud", "Suceava", "Harghita", "Brașov", "Sibiu", "Alba", "Cluj"],
  "Neamț": ["Suceava", "Iași", "Bacău", "Harghita"],
  "Olt": ["Vâlcea", "Argeș", "Teleorman", "Dolj"],
  "Prahova": ["Brașov", "Buzău", "Ialomița", "Ilfov", "Dâmbovița"],
  "Satu Mare": ["Maramureș", "Sălaj", "Bihor"],
  "Sălaj": ["Satu Mare", "Maramureș", "Cluj", "Bihor"],
  "Sibiu": ["Mureș", "Brașov", "Argeș", "Vâlcea", "Alba"],
  "Suceava": ["Botoșani", "Iași", "Neamț", "Harghita", "Mureș", "Bistrița-Năsăud", "Maramureș"],
  "Teleorman": ["Olt", "Argeș", "Dâmbovița", "Giurgiu"],
  "Timiș": ["Arad", "Hunedoara", "Caraș-Severin"],
  "Tulcea": ["Galați", "Brăila", "Constanța"],
  "Vaslui": ["Iași", "Neamț", "Bacău", "Galați"],
  "Vâlcea": ["Sibiu", "Argeș", "Olt", "Dolj", "Gorj", "Hunedoara", "Alba"],
  "Vrancea": ["Bacău", "Vaslui", "Galați", "Brăila", "Buzău", "Covasna"]
};

// BFS to find the shortest path of counties between A and B
export const getCountiesOnRoute = (start: string, end: string): string[] => {
  if (!start || !end) return [];
  if (start === end) return [start];

  // Normalizing checks
  if (!COUNTY_ADJACENCY[start] || !COUNTY_ADJACENCY[end]) {
      // Fallback if data missing: just return start and end
      return [start, end];
  }

  const queue: string[][] = [[start]];
  const visited = new Set<string>();
  visited.add(start);

  while (queue.length > 0) {
    const path = queue.shift()!;
    const node = path[path.length - 1];

    if (node === end) {
      return path;
    }

    const neighbors = COUNTY_ADJACENCY[node] || [];
    for (const neighbor of neighbors) {
      if (!visited.has(neighbor)) {
        visited.add(neighbor);
        const newPath = [...path, neighbor];
        queue.push(newPath);
      }
    }
  }

  // If no path found (island?), return just endpoints
  return [start, end];
};
```

## pages/Home.tsx
Updated to include the "Travel Mode" toggle and utilize the route graph logic.

```tsx
import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react';
import { AdCard } from '../components/AdCard';
import { Carousel, Slide } from '../components/Carousel';
import { CategoryNav } from '../components/CategoryNav';
import { fetchActiveAds } from '../services/mockBackend';
import { Ad } from '../types';
import { getCounties, getCities, getVillages } from '../data/locations';
import { getCountiesOnRoute } from '../utils/routeGraph';

interface HomeProps {
  onNavigate: (path: string) => void;
  onOpenCreateModal: () => void;
  onAdClick: (ad: Ad) => void;
  favoriteIds: string[];
  onToggleFavorite: (id: string) => void;
}

export const Home: React.FC<HomeProps> = ({ 
  onNavigate, 
  onOpenCreateModal, 
  onAdClick,
  favoriteIds,
  onToggleFavorite 
}) => {
  const [ads, setAds] = useState<Ad[]>([]);
  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true);

  // Search Mode: 'local' (Standard) or 'route' (Travel)
  const [searchMode, setSearchMode] = useState<'local' | 'route'>('local');

  // Filters
  const [searchTerm, setSearchTerm] = useState('');
  const [selectedCategory, setSelectedCategory] = useState('');
  const [showFavoritesOnly, setShowFavoritesOnly] = useState(false);

  // Local Mode State
  const [filterCounty, setFilterCounty] = useState('');
  const [filterCity, setFilterCity] = useState('');
  const [filterVillage, setFilterVillage] = useState('');
  const [availableCities, setAvailableCities] = useState<string[]>([]);
  const [availableVillages, setAvailableVillages] = useState<string[]>([]);

  // Route Mode State
  const [routeStartCounty, setRouteStartCounty] = useState('');
  const [routeEndCounty, setRouteEndCounty] = useState('');
  const [calculatedRouteCounties, setCalculatedRouteCounties] = useState<string[]>([]);

  useEffect(() => {
    const loadAds = async () => {
      try {
        const data = await fetchActiveAds();
        setAds(data);
      } catch (err) {
        console.error("Failed to load ads", err);
      } finally {
        setLoading(false);
      }
    };
    loadAds();
  }, []);

  // Cascading Filters (Local Mode)
  useEffect(() => {
    if (filterCounty) {
      setAvailableCities(getCities(filterCounty));
      setFilterCity('');
      setFilterVillage('');
      setAvailableVillages([]);
    } else {
      setAvailableCities([]);
      setFilterCity('');
      setFilterVillage('');
      setAvailableVillages([]);
    }
  }, [filterCounty]);

  useEffect(() => {
    if (filterCounty && filterCity) {
      setAvailableVillages(getVillages(filterCounty, filterCity));
      setFilterVillage('');
    } else {
      setAvailableVillages([]);
      setFilterVillage('');
    }
  }, [filterCounty, filterCity]);

  // Route Calculation
  useEffect(() => {
    if (searchMode === 'route' && routeStartCounty && routeEndCounty) {
      const path = getCountiesOnRoute(routeStartCounty, routeEndCounty);
      setCalculatedRouteCounties(path);
    } else {
      setCalculatedRouteCounties([]);
    }
  }, [searchMode, routeStartCounty, routeEndCounty]);

  const filteredAds = ads.filter(ad => {
    // 1. Keyword Search
    const matchesSearch = 
      ad.title.toLowerCase().includes(searchTerm.toLowerCase()) || 
      ad.description.toLowerCase().includes(searchTerm.toLowerCase());

    // 2. Category
    const matchesCategory = selectedCategory ? ad.category === selectedCategory : true;

    // 3. Location Logic
    const adLocation = ad.location || { county: '', city: '', village: '' };
    let matchesLocation = true;

    if (searchMode === 'local') {
      const matchesCounty = filterCounty ? adLocation.county === filterCounty : true;
      const matchesCity = filterCity ? adLocation.city === filterCity : true;
      const matchesVillage = filterVillage ? adLocation.village === filterVillage : true;
      matchesLocation = matchesCounty && matchesCity && matchesVillage;
    } else {
      // Route Mode
      if (routeStartCounty && routeEndCounty && calculatedRouteCounties.length > 0) {
        matchesLocation = calculatedRouteCounties.includes(adLocation.county);
      }
    }

    // 4. Favorites
    const matchesFavorite = showFavoritesOnly ? favoriteIds.includes(ad.id) : true;

    return matchesSearch && matchesCategory && matchesLocation && matchesFavorite;
  });

  const heroSlides: Slide[] = [
    {
      id: '1',
      image: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1488459716781-31db52582fe9?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=2000',
      title: 'Support Local Producers',
      description: 'Discover fresh, handmade, and unique products directly from the source. Join MiculProducator today.',
      ctaText: 'Start Selling Now',
      onCtaClick: onOpenCreateModal,
    },
    {
      id: '2',
      image: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1615485925763-867862780c10?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=2000',
      title: 'Fresh from the Garden',
      description: 'Find seasonal vegetables, organic fruits, and artisanal foods right in your neighborhood.',
      ctaText: 'Browse Fresh Food',
      onCtaClick: () => {
        setSelectedCategory('Legume');
        document.getElementById('listings')?.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' });
      },
    },
    {
      id: '3',
      image: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1469854523086-cc02fe5d8800?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=2000',
      title: 'Traveling across Romania?',
      description: 'Find fresh food and products along your route. Support locals wherever you go.',
      ctaText: 'Plan Route',
      onCtaClick: () => {
        setSearchMode('route');
        document.getElementById('listings')?.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' });
      },
    }
  ];

  return (
    <div className="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">

      {/* Header Carousel */}
      <Carousel slides={heroSlides} />

      {/* Visual Category Navigation */}
      <CategoryNav selectedCategory={selectedCategory} onSelectCategory={setSelectedCategory} />

      <div id="listings" className="mb-6">
        <div className="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-6 gap-4">
           <div>
             <h1 className="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Latest Listings</h1>
             <p className="text-gray-500 mt-1">Discover great deals or sell your items today.</p>
           </div>

           <div className="flex space-x-2">
            <button
               onClick={() => setShowFavoritesOnly(!showFavoritesOnly)}
               className={`flex items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-full border text-sm font-medium transition-colors ${
                  showFavoritesOnly 
                    ? 'bg-red-50 text-red-600 border-red-200' 
                    : 'bg-white text-gray-600 border-gray-300 hover:bg-gray-50'
               }`}
             >
               <svg className={`w-4 h-4 mr-2 ${showFavoritesOnly ? 'fill-current' : ''}`} fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth={2} d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" /></svg>
               {showFavoritesOnly ? 'Show All' : 'Show Favorites'}
             </button>
           </div>
        </div>

        {/* Search & Filter Bar */}
        <div className="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
           {/* Mode Toggles */}
           <div className="flex border-b border-gray-100">
             <button
                onClick={() => setSearchMode('local')}
                className={`flex-1 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-center transition-colors flex items-center justify-center ${
                  searchMode === 'local' ? 'bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 border-b-2 border-indigo-600' : 'text-gray-500 hover:bg-gray-50'
                }`}
             >
               <svg className="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth={2} d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6" /></svg>
               Find Locally
             </button>
             <button
                onClick={() => setSearchMode('route')}
                className={`flex-1 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-center transition-colors flex items-center justify-center ${
                  searchMode === 'route' ? 'bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 border-b-2 border-indigo-600' : 'text-gray-500 hover:bg-gray-50'
                }`}
             >
               <svg className="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth={2} d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" /></svg>
               On the Road (Travel Mode)
             </button>
           </div>

           <div className="p-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 animate-fade-in">
             {/* Common: Keyword Search */}
             <div>
               <label className="block text-xs font-bold text-gray-700 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Search Products</label>
               <input
                 type="text"
                 placeholder="e.g. Tomatoes, Honey..."
                 value={searchTerm}
                 onChange={(e) => setSearchTerm(e.target.value)}
                 className="w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 border p-2.5 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500"
               />
             </div>

             {searchMode === 'local' ? (
               <>
                {/* Local Filters */}
                 <div>
                   <label className="block text-xs font-bold text-gray-700 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Județ</label>
                   <select
                     value={filterCounty}
                     onChange={(e) => setFilterCounty(e.target.value)}
                     className="w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 border p-2.5 bg-white focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500"
                   >
                     <option value="">Toate Județele</option>
                     {getCounties().map(c => (
                       <option key={c} value={c}>{c}</option>
                     ))}
                   </select>
                 </div>
                 <div>
                   <label className="block text-xs font-bold text-gray-700 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Oraș (City)</label>
                    <select
                     value={filterCity}
                     onChange={(e) => setFilterCity(e.target.value)}
                     disabled={!filterCounty}
                     className="w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 border p-2.5 bg-white focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500 disabled:bg-gray-100 disabled:text-gray-400"
                   >
                     <option value="">Toate Orașele</option>
                     {availableCities.map(c => (
                       <option key={c} value={c}>{c}</option>
                     ))}
                   </select>
                 </div>
                 <div>
                   <label className="block text-xs font-bold text-gray-700 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Sat (Village)</label>
                    <select
                     value={filterVillage}
                     onChange={(e) => setFilterVillage(e.target.value)}
                     disabled={!filterCity || availableVillages.length === 0}
                     className="w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 border p-2.5 bg-white focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500 disabled:bg-gray-100 disabled:text-gray-400"
                   >
                     <option value="">Toate Satele</option>
                     {availableVillages.map(v => (
                       <option key={v} value={v}>{v}</option>
                     ))}
                   </select>
                 </div>
               </>
             ) : (
               <>
                {/* Route Filters */}
                 <div className="relative">
                   <label className="block text-xs font-bold text-gray-700 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1 flex items-center">
                     <span className="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 mr-2"></span>
                     Pornire (Start)
                   </label>
                   <select
                     value={routeStartCounty}
                     onChange={(e) => setRouteStartCounty(e.target.value)}
                     className="w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 border p-2.5 bg-white focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500"
                   >
                     <option value="">Select Județ</option>
                     {getCounties().map(c => (
                       <option key={c} value={c}>{c}</option>
                     ))}
                   </select>
                 </div>

                 <div className="flex items-center justify-center md:hidden text-gray-400">
                    <svg className="w-6 h-6 transform rotate-90" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth={2} d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" /></svg>
                 </div>

                 <div className="relative">
                   <label className="block text-xs font-bold text-gray-700 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1 flex items-center">
                     <span className="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500 mr-2"></span>
                     Destinație (End)
                   </label>
                   <select
                     value={routeEndCounty}
                     onChange={(e) => setRouteEndCounty(e.target.value)}
                     className="w-full rounded-lg border-gray-300 border p-2.5 bg-white focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500"
                   >
                     <option value="">Select Județ</option>
