To manage 1,000–2,000+ ads efficiently, the standard engineering solution is **Pagination**.

**Why Pagination is better than Infinite Scroll for Classifieds:**
1.  **Performance:** Keeps the DOM light. Rendering 2,000 complex Ad Cards will crash mobile browsers; rendering 12 at a time is instant.
2.  **Navigation:** Users can remember "I saw that tractor on Page 3" and go back.
3.  **Footer Access:** Infinite scroll makes it impossible to reach the footer (contact info, terms).

I will implement a robust **Pagination System** in `pages/Home.tsx`.

### Specification
1.  **Limit:** Show **12 ads per page**.
2.  **Auto-Reset:** If the user changes a filter (Category, Search, Location), automatically jump back to **Page 1**.
3.  **Auto-Scroll:** When clicking "Next Page", smooth scroll back to the top of the listings so the user doesn't have to scroll up manually.
4.  **UI:** A clean, centered pagination bar with "Previous", Page Numbers, and "Next".

